10.12.1.name: wordpress/gwo4wp
10.12.1.description:
This plugin integrates Google Website Optimizer with Wordpress. You don't have to change anything in your Wordpress files or templates to get this plugin to work.

You'll get a new section on the "Add new" page which is called GWO. There you just check the boxes that corresponds to your testcase.

The plugin doesn't create a test for you. You need to do that yourself on http://www.google.com/websiteoptimizer

Requirements

You must have a Google Website Optimizer account. You must have PHP5
